  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Motor Assailant</strong> is a vehicle combat game featuring 18 levels, including boss battles, set in 5 different environments. You can choose from 6 different combat vehicles, each with its own unique weapon. Your goal is to drive and shoot through each level to uncover a dark corporate secret, witness catastrophic events, and make humanity's first contact with alien life.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/852dabcadc62be8c98e250d60fd09396.poster.avif?t=1765205682\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/852dabcadc62be8c98e250d60fd09396.webm?t=1765205682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/852dabcadc62be8c98e250d60fd09396.mp4?t=1765205682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    18 levels including boss battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    5 different environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    6 unique vehicles with special weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Customize and upgrade vehicles in garage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Special weapons, mines, homing missiles, airstrikes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Giant boss fights on each planet</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Storyline with corporate secret, catastrophic events, alien life</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/25da608fdccde3bdf6e31730403f9ce3.poster.avif?t=1765205682\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/25da608fdccde3bdf6e31730403f9ce3.webm?t=1765205682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/25da608fdccde3bdf6e31730403f9ce3.mp4?t=1765205682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Every vehicle in the game has a unique weapon that requires a slightly different playstyle. You can purchase, upgrade, and customize your vehicle in the garage using cash earned during missions. Each planet contains multiple levels, culminating in a giant boss fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/4a6a6f3640c48836fbf034b00e14b231.avif?t=1765205682\" width=618 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with a vehicle-specific weapon, mines, homing missiles, and the ability to call in airstrikes, you will wreak havoc across 18 battlefields in 5 different environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/7e6aef2d28c02d27b19cf4682059b34b.avif?t=1765205682\" width=618 height=318 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/1222cdfc0361f63789cc1b463863a9d1.poster.avif?t=1765205682\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/1222cdfc0361f63789cc1b463863a9d1.webm?t=1765205682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/1222cdfc0361f63789cc1b463863a9d1.mp4?t=1765205682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a lieutenant in a private corporate military force, you will receive orders and advice from your superior officers, Colonel Schmidt and Captain Schroeder, during missions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/b93ca7708652ad20dc34ae19c4d37e38.avif?t=1765205682\" width=618 height=300 /></span>You begin your journey at a remote mining colony, where a truce with a rival corporation is in place. However, events quickly begin to unfold when a rogue comet enters the system from interstellar space. As you embark on your first mission, a simple patrol, you will find yourself fighting against enemy vehicles and turrets. But as the story progresses, you will face something that no one expected to encounter.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Motor Assailant</strong> is a vehicle combat game featuring 18 levels, including boss battles, set in 5 different environments. You can choose from 6 different combat vehicles, each with its own unique weapon. Your goal is to drive and shoot through each level to uncover a dark corporate secret, witness catastrophic events, and make humanity's first contact with alien life.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/852dabcadc62be8c98e250d60fd09396.poster.avif?t=1765205682\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/852dabcadc62be8c98e250d60fd09396.webm?t=1765205682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/852dabcadc62be8c98e250d60fd09396.mp4?t=1765205682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    18 levels including boss battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    5 different environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    6 unique vehicles with special weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Customize and upgrade vehicles in garage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Special weapons, mines, homing missiles, airstrikes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Giant boss fights on each planet</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Storyline with corporate secret, catastrophic events, alien life</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/25da608fdccde3bdf6e31730403f9ce3.poster.avif?t=1765205682\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/25da608fdccde3bdf6e31730403f9ce3.webm?t=1765205682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/25da608fdccde3bdf6e31730403f9ce3.mp4?t=1765205682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Every vehicle in the game has a unique weapon that requires a slightly different playstyle. You can purchase, upgrade, and customize your vehicle in the garage using cash earned during missions. Each planet contains multiple levels, culminating in a giant boss fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/4a6a6f3640c48836fbf034b00e14b231.avif?t=1765205682\" width=618 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with a vehicle-specific weapon, mines, homing missiles, and the ability to call in airstrikes, you will wreak havoc across 18 battlefields in 5 different environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/7e6aef2d28c02d27b19cf4682059b34b.avif?t=1765205682\" width=618 height=318 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/1222cdfc0361f63789cc1b463863a9d1.poster.avif?t=1765205682\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/1222cdfc0361f63789cc1b463863a9d1.webm?t=1765205682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/1222cdfc0361f63789cc1b463863a9d1.mp4?t=1765205682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a lieutenant in a private corporate military force, you will receive orders and advice from your superior officers, Colonel Schmidt and Captain Schroeder, during missions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1163730/extras/b93ca7708652ad20dc34ae19c4d37e38.avif?t=1765205682\" width=618 height=300 /></span>You begin your journey at a remote mining colony, where a truce with a rival corporation is in place. However, events quickly begin to unfold when a rogue comet enters the system from interstellar space. As you embark on your first mission, a simple patrol, you will find yourself fighting against enemy vehicles and turrets. But as the story progresses, you will face something that no one expected to encounter.</p>",
